From our Sponsor Boston Uncorked:

On Thursday, April 26th at the Back Bay Social Club, an entirely new National Wine Brand will be launched here in Boston.

Be one of the first to taste for only $10.00 per person and includes all the wine and food from 7:00-9:00PM. Your $10.00 donation goes to "Charity Water"!

Event limited to 125 people.

Get ticket here: http://thediviningrod.eventbrite.com/ for $10.00
item.how_to_find_us: Meet at 6:45pm in lobby or inside during the event.
